1. *Ovamo* ideš na posao. (Here you go to work.)
2. On je *ovamo* došao pre nekoliko dana. (He came here a few days ago.)
3. Trebaće nam da dođemo *ovamo* za par minuta. (We need to come here in a few minutes.)
4. *Ovamo* nisu dozvoljene vreće. (Bags are not allowed here.)
5. *Ovamo* se ide ulicom. (You go here by the street.)
6. Njegov je savet bio da idemo *ovamo* dok je još rano. (His advice was to go here while it is still early.)
7. Da li ćeš odvesti decu *ovamo* sutra? (Are you going to take the kids here tomorrow?)
8. *Ovamo* se šalje poruka. (This is where the message is sent.)